data.description: Sitting atop the mountain is a beautifully maintained custom home on 7.5 acres that showcases an expansive view of the lovely foothills surrounding it.  You'll love the light, bright airy feel of the home & the fact that lends itself perfectly to any entertaining you may want to do. Many built-in cabinets provide not only practicality but also a touch of elegance to the home.Having ample storage space is always a plus & the detail of a dedicated cabinet for a KitchenAid type mixer in the kitchen island is a thoughtful addition for any avid cook or baker.  This home was clearly designed with both functionality & style in mind.There is an isolated bedroom/bathroom that would be a great set up for guests.  Three of the four bedrooms have  bathrooms attached, the closets are cedar lined & you'll have plenty of room for your vehicles with the attached 4 car garage. The patio in the backyard is a perfect way to watch the deer meander by or to stargaze at the end of the day.  Private, peaceful & ready for all your new family memories!Located in Yosemite Lakes Park with such amenities as a 9 hole golf course, horse riding stables, pool & clubhouse.  Call your Realtor today to schedule your tour of this wonderful home.
